{"questionId":"31996060","questionHtml":"<p>Find <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">P</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong><br>attempt to solve <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math> &nbsp; <strong>OR&nbsp;&nbsp; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math><em> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>OR<br></strong>attempt to use <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo mathvariant=\"bold\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">I</mi><mo mathvariant=\"bold\">)</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math><em><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>THEN<br><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math></strong>&nbsp; and&nbsp; <strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math></strong> (or any multiple)<em><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (A1)(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math></strong></em><strong> &nbsp; OR&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for correct eigenvectors in a matrix in the correct position for their <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">D</mi></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"31996060","referenceCode":"24N.1.AHL.TZ0.11bii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find P.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.15—Eigenvalues and eigenvectors"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}